WEBVTT

00:01.039 --> 00:03.992
♪ <i>Men.</i> ♪

00:03.993 --> 00:04.872
I feel like I spent

00:04.873 --> 00:08.141
the last half hour
yodeling in a cave.

00:09.061 --> 00:10.794
I'm sorry.
It wasn't you.

00:11.708 --> 00:13.522
No, it was, it was
like licking a lollipop

00:13.523 --> 00:14.972
that never gets
any smaller.

00:14.974 --> 00:16.691
I mean, you enjoy it,

00:16.693 --> 00:19.276
but after a while you
start to crave the stick.

00:19.278 --> 00:21.428
Did I at least make
you crave the stick?

00:21.430 --> 00:23.614
You did great.

00:23.616 --> 00:26.283
I'm just a little
distracted.

00:26.285 --> 00:27.568
Is everything okay?

00:27.570 --> 00:30.938
Not really.
We need to talk.

00:30.940 --> 00:33.273
Come on. I got lockjaw
and you want to talk?

00:33.275 --> 00:35.710
I want to know where we're
going with this relationship.

00:35.712 --> 00:37.411
Do we have
any kind of future?

00:37.413 --> 00:40.114
Of course we do.
Things are good.

00:40.116 --> 00:42.083
Things are great.
Why rock the boat?

00:42.085 --> 00:44.251
I mean, I know the little
man inside your boat

00:44.253 --> 00:45.669
could use some rocking.

00:45.671 --> 00:48.422
I'm talking about making
a long-term commitment

00:48.424 --> 00:49.757
to each other.

00:49.759 --> 00:51.258
You mean like marriage?

00:51.260 --> 00:52.727
Would that be so awful?

00:52.729 --> 00:54.178
Ask my ex-wife.

00:54.180 --> 00:56.180
Her statement in court read
like a Stephen King novel.

00:56.182 --> 00:58.649
Where is this coming
from all of a sudden?

00:58.651 --> 01:00.601
It was something
my gynecologist said.

01:00.603 --> 01:02.570
Are you all right?
I'm fine.

01:02.572 --> 01:04.739
He said, "Everything looks
great down here.

01:04.741 --> 01:06.473
Would you like to
have dinner sometime?"

01:06.475 --> 01:10.477
Wow. Wow. That is
wildly inappropriate.

01:10.479 --> 01:12.913
I mean, as a
doctor myself...

01:12.915 --> 01:13.981
You're a chiropractor.

01:13.983 --> 01:15.249
Nonetheless,
I am a healer.

01:15.251 --> 01:17.368
There's a code!

01:17.370 --> 01:18.953
I mean, you don't
ask someone out

01:18.955 --> 01:21.155
when they're buck naked with
their feet in the stirrups.

01:21.157 --> 01:22.623
Unless you're drunk
at a rodeo.

01:22.625 --> 01:23.991
Well, he did.

01:23.993 --> 01:26.177
Do you want to go
out with him?

01:26.179 --> 01:28.212
It's not about
going out with him.

01:28.214 --> 01:30.598
But if you and I
don't have a future,

01:30.600 --> 01:32.332
I need to examine
my options.

01:32.334 --> 01:35.886
The way you got examined
by Dr. Busyfingers?

01:35.888 --> 01:39.640
Look, I don't want
to grow old alone.

01:39.642 --> 01:42.443
So, if you're not ready to make
this kind of commitment,

01:42.445 --> 01:44.278
better to know now.

01:44.280 --> 01:46.614
Geez, Lyndsey, you
kinda sprung this on me.

01:46.616 --> 01:50.117
I mean, I don't have to give you
an answer just this second, do I?

01:50.119 --> 01:52.820
No, no, of course not.
Just think about it.

01:52.822 --> 01:53.821
Okay.

01:53.823 --> 01:54.905
Good night.

01:54.907 --> 01:56.407
Good night.

02:01.246 --> 02:02.746
And just for the record,

02:02.748 --> 02:03.998
he gets paid to
go down there.

02:04.000 --> 02:05.716
I do it for the
love of the game.

02:07.719 --> 02:10.503
♪ Men, men, men, men, manly men,
men, men ♪

02:10.506 --> 02:13.674
♪ Ah.
♪ Men.

