02:20.177 --> 02:21.669
♪ <i>Men.</i> ♪

02:21.670 --> 02:23.036
Hey.

02:23.038 --> 02:24.588
Oh, hey, can I borrow your car?

02:24.590 --> 02:27.724
I need to take my bike into the
shop, and it won't fit in mine.

02:27.726 --> 02:28.775
Sure. No problem.

02:28.777 --> 02:29.810
Thanks.

02:29.812 --> 02:31.528
I assume it needs gas?

02:31.530 --> 02:33.947
And oil.

02:33.949 --> 02:36.066
And brake fluid.

02:36.068 --> 02:38.769
And wiper blades.

02:38.771 --> 02:40.687
So, uh, what are
you reading?

02:40.689 --> 02:42.356
I'm trying to finish <i>Ulysses.</i>

02:42.358 --> 02:43.273
Oh, that's a tough one.

02:43.275 --> 02:44.525
How long have you
been reading it?

02:44.527 --> 02:47.161
14 years.

02:47.163 --> 02:49.396
I'm on page eight.

02:49.398 --> 02:50.831
Impressive.

02:50.833 --> 02:53.267
I'm still on the first
Tuesday with Morrie.

02:53.269 --> 02:55.102
He dies in the end.

02:55.104 --> 02:57.004
Thank you.

02:57.006 --> 03:00.073
So, listen, I want to ask your
opinion about something.

03:00.075 --> 03:02.309
Lyndsey has been pushing me
to make a commitment

03:02.311 --> 03:04.278
'cause some other guy
asked her out.

03:04.280 --> 03:05.279
Who asked her out?

03:05.281 --> 03:06.580
Her gynecologist.

03:06.582 --> 03:09.850
Well, at least he knows
what he's getting into.

03:14.189 --> 03:17.091
Cute. I mean,
don't want to lose Lyndsey,

03:17.093 --> 03:19.493
but I'm just not ready
to make a commitment.

03:19.495 --> 03:21.795
Well, my advice is you better do
something soon,

03:21.797 --> 03:23.830
or you're out
and the doctor's in.

03:23.832 --> 03:26.032
And when I say,
"The doctor's in," I mean...

03:26.034 --> 03:27.767
No, I got it, I got it.

03:27.769 --> 03:29.769
All right, I got
to get out of here.

03:29.771 --> 03:31.270
Oh, here you go.

03:31.272 --> 03:33.338
Oh, uh, the driver's side door
doesn't work anymore,

03:33.340 --> 03:35.006
so either get in
the passenger side

03:35.008 --> 03:36.475
or climb in through the window.

03:37.343 --> 03:39.277
Got it.

03:39.279 --> 03:41.179
Oh, and whatever you do, when
you put the key in the ignition,

03:41.181 --> 03:42.547
make sure you're
holding something rubber.

03:42.549 --> 03:46.318
You know,
so you're grounded.

03:46.320 --> 03:48.453
Does Lyndsey
have a nice car?

03:48.455 --> 03:49.921
Yeah.
Marry her.

03:49.923 --> 03:51.890
♪ <i>Men.</i> ♪

03:51.892 --> 03:54.025
♪ And he's holding
her in his arms ♪

03:54.027 --> 03:56.060
♪ Late, late at night ♪

